    "faq.1.q": "What is 3035TECH?",
    "faq.1.a": "3035TECH is a global technology partner headquartered in Campo Bom, Brazil, with its engineering center at Hub 5796 and operations in the United States, Ireland, and Germany. Our Dublin office is the European hub for project coordination and commercial engagement — supporting clients across the EU and UK. The company provides managed squads, staff augmentation, custom software development, and support & evolution for enterprises worldwide.",
    "faq.2.q": "What services does 3035TECH offer?",
    "faq.2.a": "3035TECH offers four core services: Managed Squads (end-to-end engineering teams with full delivery ownership), Staff Augmentation (expert engineers embedded in client teams), Custom Development (web, mobile, APIs, and cloud-native platforms), and Support & Evolution (ongoing maintenance and product evolution).",
    "faq.3.q": "Where is 3035TECH located?",
    "faq.3.a": "3035TECH is headquartered at Hub 5796 in Campo Bom, Rio Grande do Sul, Brazil — our engineering center. We also operate in the United States and Germany. In Ireland, our Dublin office is the European hub for project coordination and commercial engagement, with aligned business hours and a local point of contact for clients across the EU and UK.",
    "faq.4.q": "What is nearshore staff augmentation with 3035TECH?",
    "faq.4.a": "3035TECH provides nearshore staff augmentation from Brazil and LATAM, integrating senior engineers directly into client teams. Engineers work in the same time zones as North American and European clients, with strong English proficiency and enterprise delivery experience.",
    "faq.5.q": "Which industries does 3035TECH serve?",
    "faq.5.a": "3035TECH serves enterprises across retail, fintech, healthcare, SaaS, FoodTech, and logistics. Notable clients include Arezzo, ClickFunnels, GoMoney, DoctorClin, LunchTeam, The Fruit People, and Karsten.",
