    "faq.6.a": "3035TEACH is a fully company-subsidized developer training program run by 3035TECH in Brazil. It transforms aspiring professionals into enterprise-ready full-stack engineers through technical and professional tracks. More than 80% of graduates are employed in the tech industry, with alumni at companies like SAP and Dell.",
