    "faq.7.a": "You can contact 3035TECH at contact@3035tech.com, via WhatsApp at +55 51 99644-2104, or through the contact form at 3035tech.com. The team supports English and Portuguese.",
    "faq.8.q": "Does 3035TECH work with enterprise clients globally?",
    "faq.8.a": "Yes. 3035TECH partners with global enterprises across Brazil, the United States, Europe, and other markets. Our Ireland office handles European project delivery and commercial engagement for EU and UK clients. Engagement models include managed squads, staff augmentation, custom development, and long-term support partnerships.",
    "faq.9.q": "What technologies does 3035TECH specialize in?",
    "faq.9.a": "3035TECH specializes in React, JavaScript, Java, Spring Boot, React Native, cloud-native architectures, API ecosystems, and enterprise web and mobile platforms. Teams follow agile delivery with end-to-end ownership from architecture to production.",
    "faq.10.q": "How long has 3035TECH been operating?",
    "faq.10.a": "3035TECH has been delivering technology solutions since 2015, with over 10 years of experience, 50+ projects delivered, and operations in 4 countries.",
    "faq.11.q": "Does 3035TECH use AI in software delivery?",
    "faq.11.a": "Yes, in a measured way. We use AI where it adds clear value — for example when drafting documentation, supporting implementation, and strengthening tests — always within workflows led by our engineers and subject to human review, your standards, and project policies. AI is a supporting tool for the team's work, not a replacement for engineers or for architecture and security decisions. We do not offer AI as a standalone product; we provide engineering teams that may use AI as part of their day-to-day work when it makes sense.",
    "faq.12.q": "Does 3035TECH have an office in Dublin, Ireland?",
    "faq.12.a": "Yes. 3035TECH operates a European projects and commercial hub in Dublin, Ireland. It is the local point of contact for Irish and European clients — coordinating project delivery, commercial engagement, and access to 3035TECH engineering teams in Brazil. Learn more at 3035tech.com/ireland.",
    "faq.13.q": "Does 3035TECH work with companies in Ireland and across Europe?",
    "faq.13.a": "Yes. 3035TECH partners with startups, scale-ups, and established organizations in Ireland, the EU, and the UK. Engagement models include managed squads, staff augmentation, custom software development, and long-term support — with aligned European business hours and English-speaking teams.",

    "ireland.label": "Ireland & Dublin",
    "ireland.metaTitle": "3035TECH in Ireland & Dublin — European Technology Partner",
    "ireland.metaDescription": "3035TECH's Dublin hub supports Irish and European clients with managed squads, staff augmentation, and custom software. Local commercial contact in Ireland, engineering teams in Brazil.",
    "ireland.title": "Your technology partner",
    "ireland.titleHighlight": "in Ireland and across Europe",
    "ireland.subtitle": "3035TECH's Dublin office is the European hub for project coordination and commercial engagement — connecting Irish and EU businesses with dedicated engineering teams, nearshore capacity, and enterprise delivery experience.",
    "ireland.hub.label": "Dublin hub",
    "ireland.hub.title": "European projects & commercial presence in Dublin, Ireland",
    "ireland.hub.desc": "From Dublin, 3035TECH supports clients across Ireland, the EU, and the UK with a local point of contact, aligned business hours, and direct access to senior engineers in Brazil. The hub coordinates contracts, stakeholder communication, and delivery — while squads in Campo Bom provide scalable engineering capacity.",
    "ireland.why1.title": "Local contact in Ireland",
    "ireland.why1.desc": "A Dublin-based hub for commercial engagement, project coordination, and EU/UK stakeholder alignment — without building a new engineering office from scratch.",
    "ireland.why2.title": "European business hours",
    "ireland.why2.desc": "Engineers and project leads work in overlapping hours with Ireland and continental Europe for standups, reviews, and direct collaboration with your team.",
    "ireland.why3.title": "Proven Irish client work",
    "ireland.why3.desc": "3035TECH has delivered for Dublin-based companies including LunchTeam and The Fruit People — alongside global accounts across SaaS, retail, and fintech.",
    "ireland.services.label": "Services",
    "ireland.services.title": "Engineering services for Irish & European clients",
    "ireland.services.desc": "Whether you need a fully managed squad, embedded engineers, a greenfield product build, or long-term platform support, 3035TECH combines Dublin coordination with LATAM engineering depth.",
    "ireland.clients.label": "Ireland",
    "ireland.clients.title": "Companies we support from Dublin",
    "ireland.blogLink": "European software delivery from Ireland — read the insight",
    "ireland.faq.title": "3035TECH in Ireland — common questions",
    "ireland.faq.1.q": "Where is 3035TECH located in Ireland?",
    "ireland.faq.1.a": "3035TECH's European hub is in Dublin, Ireland — coordinating project delivery and commercial engagement for clients across Ireland, the EU, and the UK. Engineering capacity is delivered by teams in Brazil with overlapping European hours.",
    "ireland.faq.2.q": "What services does 3035TECH offer in Ireland?",
    "ireland.faq.2.a": "Irish and European clients work with 3035TECH on managed squads, staff augmentation, custom software development, and support & evolution. All models include a local Dublin contact and English-speaking engineering teams.",
    "ireland.faq.3.q": "Does 3035TECH work with Irish startups and scale-ups?",
    "ireland.faq.3.a": "Yes. The Dublin hub supports startups, growing businesses, and larger enterprise accounts in Ireland — from early product builds to long-term platform teams. Contact contact@3035tech.com or use the form at 3035tech.com/contact.",
    "ireland.faq.4.q": "How do I contact 3035TECH in Ireland?",
    "ireland.faq.4.a": "Reach the 3035TECH team at contact@3035tech.com, via WhatsApp at +55 51 99644-2104, or through the contact form at 3035tech.com/contact. The Dublin hub handles European commercial engagement; support is available in English and Portuguese.",

